high_descs: Turn completely around, walk slightly forward, turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up the bowl and butter knife sitting on the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the bowl and knife in the sink, fill the sink with water.  Drain the water, and pick up the bowl and knife.
Turn right, walk slightly forward, turn right, walk to the wall, turn left and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door, put the bowl and knife on the shelf in front of the blue bowl, and close the refrigerator door.
anns.task_desc: Rinse the bowl and knife and put them in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and veer right to the wooden table.
Pick up the dirty pan near the center of the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Turn right and walk ahead, veering right to the fridge.
Place the pan in the fridge on the left shelf in front of the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean pan in a fridge.

high_descs: pick up dish and butter knife from table
wash dish and knife in sink, remove dish and knife from sink
put dish and knife inside fridge
anns.task_desc: put clean dish and knife inside fridge
